videos.description: JT Daniels barely gets the pass off for a jump ball that Michael Pittman Jr. wins over two Utah defenders for a 34-yard score.
videos.headline: Pittman makes an unbelievable grab in double coverage

videos.description: Tyler Huntley fumbles, USC's  Jay Tufele recovers and runs it in for a 48-yard score.
videos.headline: Trojans scoop and score

videos.description: Britain Covey catches a short pass and takes it 46-yards to the house.
videos.headline: Utes' WR breaks free for a 46-yard TD
